data.description: If you are looking for a well-cared-for home with a downstairs master and an open a floor plan look no further!  The first thing you will notice when entering this home is the huge vaulted ceiling in the great room with fireplace.  The designer kitchen has quartz counters, stainless appliances and excellent cabinet storage!  There is also a formal dining room and screened back porch on this level.  Upstairs you will find a loft/TV room, two bedrooms and a full bath.  Other features include a Tankless water heater, a double car garage AND a fully fenced backyard!
